Title: Beam of the Astrias
DateModified: '2019-02-21'
DatePublished: '2019-02-21'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/beam-of-the-astrias
SetInCountry: French Polynesia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Chri Hayes
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "BEAM.   \n\nINT. METEOROLOGY SHOW. IN STUDIO\n\nLARRY SPEAKS INTO THE CAMERA\
  \ in his blazer leisure suit. \n\n\nLARRY: \n\n75 years from now. ITS 180 degrees\
  \ everywhere, theres no gas. NOPE. GAS, WELL THAT WAR LASTED A YEAR. 2021 ALLAMERICAN\
  \ GASFIGHT. \nPEOPLE GOT FED UP AND ENOUGH OF EM\u2019 BOYCOTTED GAS CARS ROUND\
  \ THEIR TURF THAT THE BIG CORPS EVENTUALLY CHANGED. THERE WERE ALWAYS LIKE FIVE\
  \ OTHER TYPES OF FUEL CELLS -HYDROGEN/ELECTRICITY/SOLAR/STEAM\n\nTHE GLOBE IS NOT\
  \ WARMING....IT\u2019S ON FIRE! FROM THE INSIDEOUT! \n\nA SINGLE PHOTON TAKES 100,000\
  \ YEARS TO ESCAPE THE SUN. \n\nI DON\u2019T HAVE THAT KIND OF TIME. NOT SURE IF\
  \ YOU DO. AND I ESPECIALLY DON\u2019T IF SOME BLACK HOLE IS ON ITS WAY TO SHOVE\
  \ A YOU KNOW WHAT IN MY ASS. \n\n\n\n\n\n\nHe races home and stops in a golf course\
  \ green. Looking up at the stars he smiles\n\n\nWow\n\n\nHe bangs wife and takes\
  \ shower he\u2019s been searching for. He scratches his leg where he has alien implant..."
